nodes.bodyText:
Another - maybe better solution would be to replace the Autowired annotation with a constructor and an argument AdapterConfig, like this:
public KeycloakSpringBootConfigResolver(AdapterConfig config) {
  this.adapterConfig = config;
}

Because then, Spring will also identify, that AdapterConfig must be initialized before initializing KeycloakSpringBootConfigResolver. Because I'm not sure, if required=false really helps. But constructor injection would be fine too.
If you think, that would be better, let me know and I change the PR.

